Implement isochronous transfer mode.

Implement audio driver.

Do bandwidth accounting.

Use lock manager locks.

Use the pool allocator for TDs et al.

Merge soft_td and td in uhci.c.
      soft_qh and qh
      soft_ed and ed in ohci.c
